https://console.cloud.google.com/projectselector2/iam-admin/serviceaccounts?supportedpurview=project

ENABLE GOOGLE SHEET

https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/sheets.googleapis.com?project=anutecdmindia


for sheet 
sheets-service-account@anutecdmindia.iam.gserviceaccount.com
GOOGLE_CLIENT_EMAIL=sheets-service-account@anutecdmindia.iam.gserviceaccount.com

- Go to [Google Cloud Console → IAM & Admin → Service Accounts](https://console.cloud.google.com/iam-admin/serviceaccounts)

- Select project `anutecdmindia`

- Click __+ Create Service Account__

- Name it `sheets-service-account`

- Assign role: __Viewer__ (or no role — the key is enough for Sheets API)

- Click __Done__, then click on the new account → __Keys__ → __Add Key__ → __Create New Key__ → __JSON__

- Copy the `client_email` and `private_key` from the downloaded JSON into `.env.local`
